#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an9.29"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.29:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Sattāvāsavagga "
msgstr "3. Abodes of Sentient Beings "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Āghātavatthusutta "
msgstr "29. Grounds for Resentment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an9.29:1.1"
msgid "“Navayimāni, bhikkhave, āghātavatthūni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are nine grounds for resentment. "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni nava? "
msgstr "What nine? "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.3"
msgid "‘Anatthaṃ me acarī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati; "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They did wrong to me,’ you harbor resentment. "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.4"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me caratī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati; "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They are doing wrong to me’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.5"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carissatī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati; "
msgstr "‘They will do wrong to me’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.6"
msgid "‘piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acarī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘They did wrong to someone I love’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.7"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ caratī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘They are doing wrong to someone I love’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.8"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ carissatī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati; "
msgstr "‘They will do wrong to someone I love’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.9"
msgid "‘appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṃ acarī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘They helped someone I dislike’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.10"
msgid "‘atthaṃ caratī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘They are helping someone I dislike’ … "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.11"
msgid "‘atthaṃ carissatī’ti āghātaṃ bandhati. "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike,’ you harbor resentment. "

msgctxt "an9.29:1.12"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, nava āghātavatthūnī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the nine grounds for resentment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.29:1.13"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

